snippet.title: Skip Around the World | Finland * Suomi - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Skip Around the World walkthrough by Carmel Games:
Join Skip on his journey around the world. His trip's first destination is be Finland, where he will try to get the autograph of the sauna guru Oiva Vasta.
